Package civitas.celestis.math.matrix

Interface Matrix<N extends Number,M extends Matrix<N,M>>

Type Parameters:
N - The type of number this matrix contains
M - This matrix (the result of arithmetic operations)
All Superinterfaces:
Grid<N,M>, Iterable<N>, Numeric, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DoubleMatrix, LongMatrix
public interface Matrix<N extends Number,M extends Matrix<N,M>> extends Numeric, Grid<N,M>, Iterable<N>, Serializable
A two-dimensional array of numbers.

Since both double and long have 64 bits, this class can be used to contain two-dimensional data of up to 64 bits per element.
